# Component Standards

## Stack

React · TypeScript · Vite · Framer Motion · Tailwind CSS · Storybook

## File Structure

```
src/components/ComponentName/
  ComponentName.tsx
  ComponentName.stories.tsx
  index.ts
  types.ts
  styles.css
```

## Required Storybook Stories

Default, Mobile, Edge-case, Reduced Motion (when animation is central)
Interaction stories: HoverReveal, ClickReveal, ScrollReveal, LongText, NarrowWidth, DarkMode

## Accessibility

Keyboard navigation, prefers-reduced-motion, semantic HTML, readable contrast, touch usability

## Performance

- Transforms over layout animations (GPU-friendly)
- IntersectionObserver over scroll listeners
- No layout thrashing; memoize when appropriate
